{
  "texts": [
    "The logical form of the questions is also provided.",
    "• QuaRTz (Tafjord et al, 2019b).",
    "The QuaRTz dataset presents a novel task involving the qualitative analysis of textual relationships, where common qualitative statements are paired with contextually generated questions through crowdsourcing.",
    "For example, the qualitative statement \"Sunscreen with a higher SPF protects the skin for a longer time\" is paired with the contextual question \"Billy applies sunscreen with an SPF lower than Lucy's.",
    "Who will receive better sun protection?\"."
  ]
}